data.description: POOL PARTY ANYONE? This 4bed/2bath Glendale home is perfect for entertaining. The fully fenced backyard has a pool, covered patio, and double gates for easy access. This large corner lot has plenty of room for parking, and the double garage has built-in cabinets. The refrigerator, stove, washer, and dryer are included in the sale. There is an inside laundry room. This home has a split floorplan for privacy. The master bedroom has a full bath and walk-in closet. This home has a great location with no HOA fees! It's super close to ASU West and the Arizona Christian University. Plus, the 101 freeway and Arrowhead Towne Center Mall are just a few miles away. Watch the attached 3D Virtual Tour and walkthrough this entire home (inside and out) at your leisure. Scroll up/down to see everything!
